extends layout

block content
    .page.js-page
      // One Page Sidebar
      .one-page-sidebar
        // One Page Sidebar Header
        .one-page-sidebar-header
          // One Page Logo
          .one-page-logo
            // Logo Image
            a.logo-image(href='/recruiter')
              img(src='/images/logo2.png')
            br
            a.logo-image(href='/recruiter')
              img(src='/images/recruiter.png')
            // End of Logo Image
          // End of One Page Logo
          // One Page Meta
          // End of One Page Meta
        // End of One Page Sidebar Header
        // One Page Nav
        .one-page-nav-wrapper.js-custom-scrollbar
          ul.one-page-nav.js-one-page-nav(data-prepend-to='.js-prepend-mobile-menu')
            li.is-active
              a(href='#Careers')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-book
                | Careers
            li
              a(href='#Conversations')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-wechat
                | Conversations
            li
              a(href='#Demo')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-spinner
                | Demo
            li
              a(href='#Account')
                span.one-page-nav-icon
                  i.fa.fa-user
                | Account
                span.fa.fa-caret-down.pull-right(style='color:grey!important;')
              ul
                li
                  a(href='#Setting')
                    span.one-page-nav-icon
                      i.fa.fa-cog
                    | Setting
                li
                  a(href='#Upload_Picture\
                  ')
                    span.one-page-nav-icon
                      i.fa.fa-upload
                    | Upload Picture
                li
                  a(href='#Change_Password')
                    span.one-page-nav-icon
                      i.fa.fa-key
                    | Change Password
                li
                  a(href='#Logout')
                    span.one-page-nav-icon
                      i.fa.fa-power-off
                    | Logout
        // End of One Page Nav
        // One Page Sidebar Footer
        footer.one-page-sidebar-footer
          | All Rights Reserved.
          a(href='http://www.masymbol.com/', target='_blank') Masymbol Technologies
          |  Pvt Ltd © 2016
        // End of One Page Sidebar Footer
      // End of One Page Sidebar
      // One Page Content
      .one-page-content
        // Header
        header.header.large.header-one-page.js-header-fixed
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .row
              .col-md-3.col-sm-6.col-xs-5
                .visible-sm-block.visible-xs-block
                  // Logo Image
                  a.logo-image(href='/')
                    img.img-responsive(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/skilledtree-public/logo.png', alt='logo')
                  // End of Logo Image
              .col-md-12.col-sm-6.col-xs-7
                // Menu
                nav.right.helper
                  ul.menu.sf-menu.js-menu
                    li
                      a(href='/recruiter')
                        i.fa.fa-home.fa-lg
                    li
                      a(href='/recruiter/introduction') Introduction
                    li
                      a(href='/recruiter/jobs') Jobs
                    li
                      a(href='/recruiter/employees') Employees
                    li
                      a(href='/recruiter/resumes') Resumes
                    li
                      a.active(href='/recruiter/header') Header
                    li
                      a(href='/recruiter/dashboard')
                        | Dashboard
                // End of Menu
        // End of Header
        #content
          .container-fluid.container-spaced
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Careers.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Careers
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | In the top right header, department which you belong to will be displayed. Next to that, your careers page link is added to the icon. You can visit your company’s career page by clicking on the link. And provided you can share this link to the referral candidates for job vacancies.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/R28.png', width='100%')
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Conversations.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                br
                h1
                  | Conversations
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | Chat icon represents the conversation which you had previously with any of your colleagues by clicking it.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/messages.png', width='100%')
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Demo.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                h1
                  | Demo
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | It’s a complete help in reference to SkilledTree. You can read how SkilledTree works completely here.
            .row
              .col-md-8
                img(src='/images/R29.png', width='100%')
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Account.category-info.helper.pt0
                br
                br
                h1
                  | Account
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                br
                .row
                  .col-md-8
                    img(src='/images/R30.png', width='100%')
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Setting.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Setting
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | Major settings like Company profile, Your profile,Password and notifications will be added and modified here.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Upload_Picture.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Upload Picture
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | You can set up your personal profile picture here. It will be visible to all your members in your network for better identification.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Change_Password.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Change Password
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | You can reset your password even if you are not sure. It will be automatically popped up the current password. So you can reset it easily.
            .col-md-12
              // Category Info
              #Logout.category-info.helper.pt0
                h1
                  | Logout
                  // Fragment Identifier
                  // End of Fragment Identifier
                p.category-content
                  | If want to sign out the SkilledTree session. You can!
    // End of One Page Content
